flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 34: RAG Semantic Search, Opportunity, and Bundle Intelligence Flow

  subgraph RAG[RAG Semantic Search Pipeline]
    Q[User query\nGET /api/search/semantic?q=...] --> E[Generate embeddings]
    E --> VEC[pgvector cosine similarity]
    Q --> LEX[Meilisearch lexical query]
    VEC --> FUSION[Reciprocal Rank Fusion]
    LEX --> FUSION
    FUSION --> RANKED[Ranked semantic + lexical results]
  end

  subgraph OPP[Opportunity Engine Pipeline]
    OCron[15-min CRON] --> OScan[Scan vendor portfolio\nstock, demand, price signals]
    OScan --> OClass[Classify alerts\nred/yellow/green/blue]
    OClass --> OPersist[(Write opportunity_alerts)]
    OPersist --> OAction[Recommend price, flash sale, bundle, restock]
  end

  subgraph BUNDLE[Bundle Recommendation Pipeline]
    BCron[Weekly CRON] --> CoBuy[Build co-purchase matrix\nfrom order_items]
    CoBuy --> BScore[Category affinity scoring]
    BScore --> BPersist[(Write bundle_suggestions)]
    BPersist --> BTop[Top 5 bundle suggestions\nwith 5-15% discount]
  end

  Dashboard[Vendor Dashboard]
  Sahayak[Sahayak Context and Tools]

  RANKED --> Dashboard
  OAction --> Dashboard
  BTop --> Dashboard

  RANKED --> Sahayak
  OAction --> Sahayak
  BTop --> Sahayak

  VecFail{Embedding index stale?}
  OppFail{Opportunity scan missed cycle?}
  BundleFail{Bundle compute failure?}
  RFallback[Serve lexical-only fallback\nwith stale-warning]

  VEC --> VecFail
  VecFail -- Yes --> Regen[Queue embedding regeneration]
  Regen --> RFallback
  RFallback --> Dashboard
  RFallback --> Sahayak
  VecFail -- No --> RANKED

  OScan --> OppFail
  OppFail -- Yes --> OStale[Mark alert set stale\nretry scheduler]
  OStale --> Dashboard
  OStale --> Sahayak
  OppFail -- No --> OClass

  CoBuy --> BundleFail
  BundleFail -- Yes --> BSnapshot[Retain last successful\nbundle snapshot with timestamp]
  BSnapshot --> Dashboard
  BSnapshot --> Sahayak
  BundleFail -- No --> BScore
